<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Asleep" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Asleep,</orth> 1) in sleep, sleeping: <cit><quote>lying once a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 154.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 154, 1</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.232" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 232</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.191" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 191</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.191" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 191</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.191" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 191</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.2.155" default="NO" valid="yes">2, 155</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.2.68" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 68</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.2.68" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 68</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.98.68" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 98</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.1.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. III, 1, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.2.136" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 136</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 3.3.71" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 3, 71</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.177" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 177</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.2.101" default="NO" valid="yes">2, 101</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 4.1.133" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 133</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 4.1.133" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 133</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.331.133" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 331</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.151" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 151</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.3.221" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 3, 221</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.577" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 577</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.2.122" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 2, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.249" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 249</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.96" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 96</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 4.2.81" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 IV, 2, 81</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.5.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 5, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.3.89" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 3, 89</bibl> <cit><quote>(when he is drunk a.).</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 4.2.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 2, 97</bibl></cit>, etc. <emph>got 'tween a. and wake</emph> (== between a. and awake) <bibl n="shak. lr 1.2.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 2, 15</bibl>. Figuratively: <cit><quote>though credit be a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 5.2.67" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. V, 2, 67</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>their pride and mettle is a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.3.22" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 3, 22</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) into sleep: <cit><quote>fall a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 153.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 153, 1</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.112" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 112</bibl>. <cit><quote>laugh me a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.189" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 1, 189</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>sing me a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 2, 7</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.163" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 3, 163</bibl>. <cit><quote>rock me a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.211" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 211</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>lull a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 3.2.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. III, 2, 115</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to bring her babe a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 29</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>sucks the nurse a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.313" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 313</bibl></cit> etc.
